-------bitwise operation---------
&(binary and)
|(binary or)
^(binary xor)
~(negation)
<<(left shift)
>>(right shif)
------logical operation----------
and
or
not
-------membership operator-----------
in
not in
       eg :x=[2,34,5,1,]
       2 in x =true
       8 in x =flase
       2 not in x =flase
       8 not in x = true
----------identity operation-----------
is 
is not
     eg: x1=5
         y1=5
         x2='hello'
         y2="hello"
         print(x1 is not y1) # false
         print(x2 is y2)     #True
